_sText:
**-24 spawns among 2 rooms, and 2 spawns above main spawn rooms, for each side(26 for each side, and 52 for whole map)**

**-Dev textures, and great lighting**

**-Only 8mb uncompressed**

**-Optimized fully, to ensure good framerates**

I've worked on this map for quite some time now, and it came out fairly well. I can't wait for you all to play it. This is my first map, and I consider it well-done to my standards.(Which are very high) I know that i'm still learning though, so if you got any pointers feel free to give me some.


-Quick thank you to [www.bor3dgaming.com](http://www.bor3dgaming.com "www.bor3dgaming.com") for being great community and my support throughout creating this map.
